{"prompt": "Develop a comprehensive platform for a corporate event planner. The primary color should be a sophisticated dark teal.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Corporate Event Planner</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #008080; /* Dark Teal */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #006a6a; /* Slightly darker teal */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #a0d2db; /* Lighter teal for hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #008080; /* Dark Teal */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #008080;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item, .feature-item, .contact-info, .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .service-item h3, .feature-item h3 {\n            color: #006a6a;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #008080; /* Dark Teal */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #006a6a; /* Slightly darker teal */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        input[type=\"text\"], input[type=\"email\"], textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        textarea {\n            height: 120px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #008080; /* Dark Teal */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elegance Events & Planning</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Unforgettable Corporate Experiences</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#features\">Why Choose Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Your Vision, Our Expertise</h2>\n            <p>We specialize in transforming your corporate event ideas into seamless realities. From intimate board meetings to grand product launches, we handle every detail with precision and creativity.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Event Strategy & Concept Development</h3>\n                <p>Collaborative planning to define event goals, target audience, and unique themes.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Venue Selection & Management</h3>\n                <p>Sourcing and securing the perfect location, negotiating contracts, and managing logistics.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Logistics & Operations</h3>\n                <p>Comprehensive planning for A/V, catering, transportation, staffing, and on-site coordination.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Speaker & Entertainment Booking</h3>\n                <p>Identifying and securing engaging speakers, performers, and facilitators.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Marketing & Communications</h3>\n                <p>Developing invitation strategies, promotional materials, and event websites.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Budget Management</h3>\n                <p>Meticulous tracking and management of all event expenditures to ensure fiscal responsibility.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"features\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Elegance Events?</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Meticulous Attention to Detail</h3>\n                <p>We believe that the little things make the biggest difference. From the initial concept to the final farewell, no detail is too small for our team.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Tailored Solutions</h3>\n                <p>Every event is unique. We work closely with you to understand your specific needs and craft a bespoke plan that aligns with your brand and objectives.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Trusted Network</h3>\n                <p>Leveraging our extensive network of vendors, venues, and talent ensures you receive the best quality and service at competitive prices.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Stress-Free Execution</h3>\n                <p>Our experienced team manages all aspects of your event, allowing you to focus on networking, engaging with your guests, and achieving your business goals.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Let's Plan Your Next Event</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p>Ready to create an extraordinary corporate event? Get in touch with us today!</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@eleganceevents.com</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            </div>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elegance Events & Planning. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}